Telkom has received a new number range, according to an email sent from Telkom to business partners which MyBroadband has seen. The email states that Telkom was allocated new numbers in the 067 range by ICASA. The sub range is 600 000 to 799 999, which is a size of 2,000,000, added the email. Telkom already has mobile numbers in the 0670-0672 range, as well as numbers in the 0658–0659 range. ICASA was asked to confirm the allocation, by the authority did not immediately reply to requests for comment.